{"slug":"over-run-over","title":{"en":"Over Run Over","km":"បេសកកម្មឆ្លងពេល"},"description":{"en":"While on patrol, EU sergeant Ling San Fung and her team are called to assist in a criminal chase. A gunfight breaks out, and her father is tragically killed by a stray bullet. As San Fung continues the pursuit, a mysterious natural phenomenon suddenly transports her back in time—to April 1st, three days before the incident. Realizing she can now time-travel, she sets out to prevent her father's death. However, changing the past comes at a cost. Her actions trigger a chain of unforeseen consequences. A village chief known as “Ditch,” an ICAC informant, uncovers her secret and uses her ability to investigate corrupt officers—while hiding a dark secret of his own. San Fung soon learns she isn’t the only one who can manipulate time—and that altering the past doesn’t guarantee control over the future.","km":"សាច់រឿងនិយាយពីពេលបំពេញតួនាទី ពលបាល Ling Sun Fun និងក្រុមរបស់នាងកំពុងប្រមាញ់ឧក្រិដ្ឋ។ មានការផ្ទុះកាំភ្លើងកើតឡើង Sun-Fung បានបាត់បង់ឪពុករបស់នាង។ Sun-Fung បន្តការតាមចាប់ ប៉ុន្ដែស្រាប់តែមានអព្ភូហេតុធម្មជាតិចម្លែកកើតឡើងលើនាង ហើយនាំនាងទៅថ្ងៃ១ ខែមេសា បីថ្ងៃមុនថ្ងៃកើតហេតុ។ នាងក៏ប្រើឳកាសនេះ ដើម្បីជួយជីវិតឪពុកនាង។"},"poster":"https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/hNoAAOSwGedkN7Em/s-l400.jpg","year":2022,"rating":7.5,"genres":["ACTION","COMEDY","DRAMA","HORROR","ROMANCE","THRILLER","FANTASY"],"language":"English","episodeCount":22,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/dm/refs/heads/over01/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/dm/refs/heads/over02/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"3","title":{"en":"Episode 3","km":"ភាគទី3"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ipro855/dm/refs/heads/over03/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"4","title":{"en":"Episode 4","km":"ភាគទី4"},"url":